    <p class="description">A <strong>small preview image</strong> that represents a piece of content — a video, blog post, or social media item — in feeds and search results. Thumbnails are the primary visual cue determining whether someone clicks. A great thumbnail can <strong>double click-through rate</strong> over an auto-generated frame.</p>
